# Tech Stack

## Core
- **Next.js 14** (App Router) - React framework
- **TypeScript 5.2** - Type safety
- **React 18.2** - UI library
- **Node.js >=18.17.0** - Runtime

## State Management
- **Redux Toolkit 2.2** - State management
- **Redux Persist 6.0** - State persistence (main: currencyRates, shopView; auth: token, localStorageCart)
- **Redux Thunk 3.1** - Async actions

## Forms & Validation
- **React Hook Form 7.53** - Form handling
- **Zod 3.23** - Schema validation
- **@hookform/resolvers 3.9** - Zod integration

## Styling
- **Tailwind CSS 3.3** - Utility-first CSS
- **@tailwindcss/forms 0.5** - Form styling
- **Lucide React 0.400** - Icon library
- **clsx 2.0** - Conditional classnames

## UI Components
- **React Table 7.8** - Table component
- **React Select 5.8** - Select dropdowns
- **React Modal 3.16** - Modal dialogs
- **React Datepicker 7.4** - Date selection
- **React Slick 0.30** - Carousel/slider
- **React Toastify 10.0** - Toast notifications
- **Recharts 2.12** - Charts/graphs

## Utilities
- **Axios 1.6** - HTTP client (configured with baseURL: `${process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API}/api`)
- **Lodash 4.17** - Utility functions
- **use-debounce 10.0** - Debounce hooks
- **jsbarcode 3.11** - Barcode generation
- **react-responsive 10.0** - Responsive utilities

## Analytics & Monitoring
- **@vercel/analytics 1.4** - Analytics
- **@vercel/speed-insights 1.0** - Performance monitoring

## Database
- **@vercel/postgres 0.5** - PostgreSQL client

## Environment Variables
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API` - Backend API base URL
- `NP_API_KEY` - Nova Poshta API key
- `CURRENCY_CACHE_TTL_MS` - Currency cache TTL (default: 30 minutes)
